name: San La Muerte / Give Him your offerings
description:
In his sanctuaries and altars you'll find him standing there with his magnificent presence surrounded by candles, flowers, food, money, catholic figures and also by other less ordinary offerings such as bullets, beer, liquor, cigarettes and phones. 

This piece is part of my contribution to "Our Myths" event held by Chen >>> https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/365336
